        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Modularization, state management, dependency inversion, and scalable patterns.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Performance & Reliability</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Rendering, jank elimination, startup time, memory, networking, offline and error handling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Developer Productivity</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">CI workflows, code quality, testing strategies, tooling and mentoring.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded bg-primary px-5 py-3 text-white hover:bg-secondary">Discuss your needs</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>